APR FC vs Rwamagana City

APR FC 2-0 Rwamagana City

Uko umukino uri kugenda

16:57

APR FC itangiye neza mu gikombe cy'Amahoro

APR FC itsinze umukino ubanza w'ijonjora ribanziriza 1/8 mu gikombe c'Amahoro ku bitego 2-0. Umukino wo kwishyura uzakiwa na Rwamagana City FC ku wa Gatandatu ari nabwo hazamenyakana uko amakipe azahura muri icyo cyiciro gikurikira nyuma y'umukino uzahuza Rayon Sports na AS Kigali.

Marines FC 2-0 Etincelles FC

16:52

Umukino urarangiye

Umukino waberaga i Nyamirambo urangiye APR FC itsinze ibitego 2-0 byabonetse mu gice cya mbere.

Rwamagana City nayo ihise ikora contre-attaque, Byukusenge Jean Pierre ahinduye umupira mwiza mu rubuga rw'amahina, Muganuza Jean Pierre ashyizeho umutwe ujya hejuru y'izamu.

15:06

3' igitego cya APR FC

Hakizimana Muhadjiri afunguye amazamu ku ruhande rwa APR FC ku mupira w'umuterekano wari uteretse inyuma gato y'urubuga rw'amahina, ahagana ku ruhande. Arawuteye umunyezamu Tuyisenge Eric ntiyamenya uko bigenze,yisanga inshundura zinyeganyega. Muhadjiri ntiyiriwe yishimira iki gitego.

15:04

1' APR FC ihushije igitego

APR FC ifashe umupira, ihita ikora contre-attaque, Ntwari Evode uzamutse yiruka ahindura umupira mu izamu, Danny ntiyawugeraho, ukorwaho na Muhadjiri usanga umunyezamu Tuyisenge Olivier awufata neza.

15:03

Umukino uratangiye

Umusifuzi wo hagati atangije umukino. Saleh wa Rwamagana City ateye umupira bwa mbere akinana na kapiteni we Olivier, APR FC ihita ifata umupira.

14:54

Amakipe atatu niyo azasezererwa muri iki cyiciro

Mu gihe amakipe 20 ariyo yinjiye mu ijonjora ribanza ry'igikombe cy'Amahoro ndetse Sunrise FC ikaba yarivanye mu irushanwa. bivuze ko amakipe icyenda yatsinze aziyongera kuri Espoir FC.

Nyuma y'aho bazareba amakipe atandatu atandatu yatsinzwe gake (best loosers) muri aya icyenda ari gukina, maze yiyongere kuri ya yandi 10 yatsinze, batombore muri 1/8 ku wa Gatandatu.

14:48

Ikaze kuri Stade ya Kigali i Nyamirambo

Tubahaye ikaze kuri Stade ya Kigali i Nyamirambo hagiye kubera umukino w'ijonjora ribanza ry'igikombe cy'Amahoro 2019 hagati ya APR FC na Rwamagana City.
Umukino uratangira saa 15:00.

APR FC, Rwamagana City kimwe n'ayandi makipe arimo arahatanira guhagararira u Rwanda muri CAF Confederation Cup 2019/20 mu gihe Rayon Sports izakina CAF Champions League.
